A)How to compile and run hymod demo with ifort in Linux
option 1) use makefile.hymod_ifort
to compile using makefile with ifort
  1) make -f makefile.hymod_ifort
  2) ./hymod_demo.exe
to remove intermediate files
  1) make -f makefile.hymod_ifort clean

option 2) manually create a bash file for compiling hymod demo
bash  ./hymod_ifort.sh
./hymod_demo.exe

  
option 3) automatically generate bash file for compiling hymod demo
make -f makefile.hymod_ifort clean
make -f makefile.hymod_ifort -n >hymod_ifort.sh
chmod +x hymod_ifort.sh
bash ./hymod_ifort.sh
./hymod_demo.exe

B)How to compile and run hymod demo with ifort in Windows
option 1) use hymod_ifort.bat
option 2) use VS+IVF

C)How to compile and run hymod demo with gfortran in Linux
option 1) use makefile.hymod_gfortran
to compile and run using makefile with gfortran
  1) make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran
  2) ./hymod_demo.exe
to remove intermediate files
  1) make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran clean
  
option 2) manually create a bash file for compiling hymod demo
bash  ./hymod_gfortran.sh
./hymod_demo.exe

option 3) automatically generate batch file for compiling hymod demo
make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran clean
make -f makefile.hymod_gfortran -n >hymod_gfortran.sh
chmod +x hymod_gfortran.sh
bash ./hymod_gfortran.sh
./hymod_demo.exe

D)How to compile and run hymod demo with gfortran in Windows
option 1) use hymod_gfortran.bat
option 2) use gfortran command prompt